  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: c513d81420ae4244ea5fa86c11a4a29b, type: 3}
  m_Name: GSWGA_C1_L1_Start_Dialog
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::DialogData
  lines:
  - This museum is so empty!
  - Oh hey traveller, are you able to help us?
  - In front of me is a painting which if you solve the puzzles below it correctly,
    it will reveal itself. Please have a go!
  - If you get stuck or don't know the answers, have a look around and talk to one
    of my assistants, they can provide you with useful information.
  - Lastly, there are completed puzzle paintings scattered around the musuem to show
    you what you need to create. They should come in handy if you are unable to complete
    the puzzle.
